$ perfmon.exe

  Show Resource view:
code {
C:\> perfmon /res
code }

  Start the *System Diagnostic Data Collector Set* and then display a report of its results:
code {
C:\> perfmon /report
code }

  Start the *reliability monitor*:  
code {
C:\> perfmon /rel
code }

  Start the *performance monitor*:
code {
C:\> perfmon /sys
code }

`perfmon.exe` starts the → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/perfmon_msc[`perfmon.msc`] snap in.

gh|Windows-Pics|/Windows/System32/perfmon.exe/root.png||

sa:

  → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/resmon_exe[`resmon.exe`], the *Resource Monitor*.

  → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/typeperf_exe[`typeperf.exe`]

  → Windows/dirs/PerfLogs/System/Diagnostics
